dct_description_sm: Rom. de Hooge inventor et fecit ; I. Lindenberg excudit cum privilegio.
Coordinates approximate and based on Greenwich meridian.

4 pictorial vignettes: Orbis per creationem institutus/Adam en syne scheppinge -- Per leg em constitutus/Moses en syne wetgeyinge -- Orbis per diluvium destitutus/Noah en syne danksegginge -- Per christum restitutus/Cristus en syne yerlossinge.
Shows topography, drainage, vegetation, places of historical interest.
Features an illustration of a compass rose.
